# Public repo deny-list (mirrors validate-publish.py PUBLIC_DENYLIST).
# Mechanical guard so accidental `git add` of a non-shipped artifact is
# refused at staging time rather than only by the publish skill's
# verification step.

# Submission sources (PDFs are shipped; sources are not)
submission/*.typ
submission/*.bib
submission/paper.pdf
submission/paper.md
submission/paper-draft.md
submission/oeis-draft.txt
submission/oeis-copy-helper.html
submission/reviews/

# Internal-only research artefacts
research/working-notes/
research/session-digest.md
research/session-learnings.md
research/verification-report.md
research/conjecture-report.md
research/creative-review.md
research/design-rationale.md
research/validation-report.md
research/review-*.md
research/solver-review/
research/solver-summary-log.txt
research/*-understanding.pdf
research/*-understanding.typ

# Internal test code
code/verify_method2.py

# Python build artefacts
__pycache__/
*.pyc
